    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Monastery: Ora et Labora》是一款管理类游戏，你将在其中建造并管理一座中世纪修道院。作为新任院长，你将在宁静的修道院中开始旅程，引导修士遵循神圣的“Ora et Labora”规则——也就是祈祷和劳动。管理他们的日常生活，包括进行宗教仪式、酿造优质麦酒、抄写精美手稿，同时合理调配修道院的资源。在中世纪的恶劣天气与战争威胁等各种考验面前做出关键决策，守护社区的未来。自由规划并扩展修道院，满足日益壮大的修士团体的需求，在这个渴求指引的世界中成为希望的灯塔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179120/extras/36b51f583da2b1c2713f31674b80feda.webp?t=1770739937\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179120/extras/a46487fbfd38a375ef8e5ffe4cd99527.poster.avif?t=1770739937\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179120/extras/a46487fbfd38a375ef8e5ffe4cd99527.webm?t=1770739937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179120/extras/a46487fbfd38a375ef8e5ffe4cd99527.mp4?t=1770739937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理修道院的重要资源，包括食物、水、草药和工具。平衡资源的生产和消耗，确保社区的繁荣，同时坚持修道院的核心价值——简朴与自给自足。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179120/extras/327c6fdfa01aafbe2a8ad8e4580ad85a.webp?t=1770739937\" width=600 height=60 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179120/extras/fcea3a70bbdac717ed05533b44c3c6f8.poster.avif?t=1770739937\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179120/extras/fcea3a70bbdac717ed05533b44c3c6f8.webm?t=1770739937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179120/extras/fcea3a70bbdac717ed05533b44c3c6f8.mp4?t=1770739937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 建造新房间和添加装饰元素来扩展修道院，并增添属于你的个人风格。每一项新增内容不仅会提升修道院的功能性，还能体现修道生活的精神之美与宁静氛围。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179120/extras/dc1193694d30a055904460ba0c965c41.webp?t=1770739937\" width=600 height=60 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179120/extras/6f93f545962be95a9892464f5b04a720.poster.avif?t=1770739937\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179120/extras/6f93f545962be95a9892464f5b04a720.webm?t=1770739937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179120/extras/6f93f545962be95a9892464f5b04a720.mp4?t=1770739937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 引导修士进行祈祷，以影响修道院及其周围世界的生活。虔诚的祈祷可以阻止灾难、带来好运，并营造积极的氛围。通过专注于祈祷，你可以帮助社群走向和平与繁荣。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179120/extras/9cd5cff27dd60b16ea1a77edf6d24494.webp?t=1770739937\" width=600 height=60 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179120/extras/576452a6e248d48114f4e9feea14ac32.poster.avif?t=1770739937\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179120/extras/576452a6e248d48114f4e9feea14ac32.webm?t=1770739937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179120/extras/576452a6e248d48114f4e9feea14ac32.mp4?t=1770739937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 分配修士从事农耕、手工制作和酿酒等各种任务。他们的劳动有助于修道院的成长与繁荣。合理规划工作，充分利用他们的技能，并满足社区的需求。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179120/extras/7665e339519e1dcd8470acca65ac7afb.webp?t=1770739937\" width=600 height=60 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179120/extras/22dcbd1fa2c3916807ee183a829be0b2.poster.avif?t=1770739937\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179120/extras/22dcbd1fa2c3916807ee183a829be0b2.webm?t=1770739937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179120/extras/22dcbd1fa2c3916807ee183a829be0b2.mp4?t=1770739937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 面对来自修道院内外的突发挑战和机遇。从恶劣天气和朝圣者来访，到精神危机和道德困境，你的每个决定都将影响修道院的未来。</p>",
